  typeSpeed: 0.03
  experimentDialogue: After answering the question about melting ice correctly, the
    detective looks around the laboratory for more clues. After a short search, the
    detective finds the missing experiment inside a temperature-controlled cabinet.
    Why is it inside here?
  teacherDialogue1: Excellent deduction using scientific reasoning, Detective! The
    main experiment wasn't stolen
  teacherDialogue2: I saw the students' practice ice melting because the lab is too
    warm today. I moved the real experiment into this temperature-controlled cabinet
    so it wouldn't melt too.
